data.description: WOW! 3 bed 3 bath open floor plan with soaring ceilings, cozy  brick fireplace and large living space. Updated Kitchen with granite countertops, pantry, Abundant cabinetry,  wood flooring, all appliances, and walks out to big composite deck overlooking treed area and you can enjoy the amazing sunsets!.  Finished  lower walk-out with rec-room, walk-in closet & Bathroom! Primary bedroom has nice double closets, large 3/4 bathroom and 2 other large bedrooms on this level.  Roof 6 years old, furnace & air 2015 & water heater 2018. Laundry room bonus room in lower level can be storage or workout room. This walk-out has a great patio over looking the trees. Minutes to the Hospital, Schools, Parks, Shopping, Offutt AFB, so much to offer.
